### Quiz Test API Endpoints

### Database Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/test/db/health

### List Database Tables
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/test/db/tables

### Check Quiz Table Structure
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/test/db/quiz-table

### Quiz API Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/test/quiz/health

### Test Ultra Simple Quiz (Recommended to test first)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/test/quiz/test-ultra-simple
Content-Type: application/json

### Test Simple Quiz
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/test/quiz/test-simple
Content-Type: application/json

### Test Minimal Quiz
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/test/quiz/test-minimal
Content-Type: application/json

### Create Math Quiz
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/test/quiz/create-math-quiz
Content-Type: application/json

### Create Geography Quiz
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/test/quiz/test-geography
Content-Type: application/json

### Create Sample Quiz
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/test/quiz/create-sample
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Sample Data (GET request to see the structure)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/test/quiz/sample-data

### Create Custom Quiz
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/test/quiz/create
Content-Type: application/json

